        "content": "**Example frontend / RUM** — browser health for the demo stack (not a hosted APM product).\n\nOpen http://localhost and interact with the chat. **Core Web Vitals** flow via the lib `webVitals` exporter → `sevo_web_vital` → OTel metrics. **JS errors** are captured by Grafana Faro → Loki. **Fetch traces** (e.g. Rasa) appear in Tempo via OTel `FetchInstrumentation`.\n\nFor conversation turns and phases, use **Semantic Event Observability**. For service uptime, use **Example uptime**.",
